{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "法尔提 第5话 战士的本性",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "与帝国军交战的几天后",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "魔龙，你的伤也好得差不多了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "抱歉……\\n给你添麻烦了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "虽然我被附身前的记忆很模糊……\\n但我竟会任凭黑暗魔力侵蚀，\\n看来还有待提升啊……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "这股气息……\\n是红衣骑士吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "既然要疗养，\\n留在圣城不就好了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "我不能再给你们\\n添麻烦了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "那件事已经过去了吧？\\n你也向大家道歉了啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "而且王子他们也接受了你的道歉，\\n最重要的是你失去理智\\n是黑暗魔力导致的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "你完全不需要有所顾忌。\\n圣城的各位都很想听你\\n讲讲你那些英勇事迹呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "即便如此，\\n我也不能接受你们的好意。\\n况且我不习惯和别人太亲近。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "那真是遗憾。话说，\\n接下来你有什么打算？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "我要继续旅行。\\n最快明天就会出发。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "是吗。不过，在此之前\\n你还有事要做吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "有事要做？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "和王子决斗啊。\\n你不是为了这个\\n才来圣城的吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "给人添了麻烦之后\\n还要求决斗……\\n也未免太自私了吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "王子已经答应了哦。\\n我向他说明了\\n你来到圣城的目的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "你是在顾虑我的感受吗？\\n如果是，那完全没必要。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "你可别误会。\\n这只是我的私心而已。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "你的……私心？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "我想让大家都见识一下\\n你真正的实力。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "因为我想自豪地\\n告诉大家“在竞技杯上\\n打败我的是堂堂正正的强者”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "而且我希望打败我的对手\\n一直保持强大的实力和高尚的品格。\\n不然的话就没有“追赶的价值”了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "红衣骑士……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "还是说“天空的霸主”\\n没有气度听取\\n手下败将的蠢话呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "哼……你都说到这个份上了，\\n我怎么能退缩。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "明明没必要特意与她一战的，\\n少爷还真是个老好人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "米科特",
            "context": "不，王子并不是出于好心\\n才答应决斗的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110307_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "维克托",
            "context": "败北分两种——\\n败得心服口服或心有不服。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110307_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "维克托",
            "context": "不光是我们，王子也被\\n黑暗魔力附身的“天空的霸主”\\n压制住了。但是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "米科特",
            "context": "那并不是骑士真正的力量，\\n如果不见识一下她真正的实力，\\n我们也没有办法信服。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "哈哈哈……\\n这是战士的本性吗？\\n我这个宫廷魔法师理解不了呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "我来担任裁判。\\n两位，准备好了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，我会全力以赴。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "就让我这柄枪\\n见识一下你的全力吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "预备……开始！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "呵，真不愧是龙之力！\\n相当漂亮的一击！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "和被黑暗魔力侵蚀的时候\\n截然不同！\\n动作犀利又迅捷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "那位大姐果然很厉害啊！\\n仅凭自身的力量，\\n就足以抗衡龙之力！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "但是，殿下也毫不示弱呢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110260_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾玛",
            "context": "加油！王子！\\n加油！法尔提！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "哼哼，好久没这样热血沸腾过了。\\n不过，是时候决出胜负了吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊！下一击定胜负吧！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "龙卷风扫尾！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "天霸魔龙枪！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "我的羽翼，坚不可摧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "治疗完毕。\\n你也真是的，太逞强了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "啊哈哈，对不起。\\n但我想跟她来一场\\n拼尽全力的较量。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那场决斗中我已经\\n展现出了“目前”的全力。\\n真是打得酣畅淋漓。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110260_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾玛",
            "context": "不知道法尔提\\n现在飞到哪里了呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "是啊，到哪里了呢。\\n不过我们一定会再见。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110259_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "丽雅",
            "context": "因为……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "嗯？怎么了，魔龙？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "你说我好像很开心？\\n呵……那是自然。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "王子的龙化之力虽然还不成熟，\\n但经过一番磨练后\\n想必还会继续成长吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "而且离开圣城的时候，\\n那位红衣骑士丽雅对我说。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "无论是她还是伙伴们，\\n下次相会的时候\\n一定会比现在更强大。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "那么多人拥有超越我的潜力。\\n没什么比这更令人开心的了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "话说……\\n我听说在某个遗迹里\\n沉睡着拥有强大力量之人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "就让我来检验一下\\n那个人有多大能耐吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110272_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔提",
            "context": "好了……魔龙，我们走！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}